00:00:00.161 --> 00:00:08.311
 Assalamu Alaikum, today i am how to cook DEGGI CHICKEN. 

00:00:08.311 --> 00:00:20.085
three skineless chicken.

00:00:20.085 --> 00:00:23.311
1 kg yogurt.

00:00:23.311 --> 00:00:30.475
1 large lemon.

00:00:30.475 --> 00:00:41.060
2 tbs of coriander powder,2 tbs cumin powder and crushed red chilly  2 tbs.

00:00:41.060 --> 00:00:46.554
1 ts of red chilly powder,1 1/2 ts salt,1 1/2 ts garam masala  powder.

00:00:46.554 --> 00:01:00.971
add the lemon juice on the chicken.

00:01:00.971 --> 00:01:07.067
add lemon and leave the chicken for 5 mins.

00:01:07.067 --> 00:01:22.763
after 5 mins, add yogurt in a pan,

00:01:22.763 --> 00:01:38.613
also the red chilly, salt and garam masala.

00:01:38.613 --> 00:01:49.958
coriander powder, cumin powder and crushed red chilly.

00:01:49.958 --> 00:01:58.021
mix it well.

00:01:58.021 --> 00:02:07.149
and add the remaining lemon juice .

00:02:07.149 --> 00:02:15.881
mix again.

00:02:15.881 --> 00:02:24.279
and then add the chicken one by one.

00:02:24.279 --> 00:02:35.562
now on the stove

00:02:35.562 --> 00:02:47.120
and add oil 1 1/2 cups 

00:02:47.120 --> 00:03:08.495
and let it cook, in steam no water is add

00:03:08.495 --> 00:03:22.303
it will get cooked in 20 to 25 mins

00:03:22.303 --> 00:03:41.264
2 to 3 mins u will see the yogurt bubbling

00:03:41.264 --> 00:03:57.307
once starts bubbling lower the heat to medium

00:03:57.307 --> 00:04:07.151
cover and cook for 20 mins

00:04:07.151 --> 00:04:21.635
and change sides every 10 mins

00:04:21.635 --> 00:04:32.518
i have changed the side u can see 

00:04:32.518 --> 00:05:01.728
in abroad chicken cooks faster 

00:05:01.728 --> 00:05:08.461
in india or pakistan it takes longer 

00:05:08.461 --> 00:05:20.089
pierce the chicken if tender trun the flame high to dry the water 

00:05:20.089 --> 00:05:30.711
when the water dries your chicken is ready.

00:05:30.711 --> 00:05:35.476
garnish it with fresh coriander and green chilly. 

00:05:35.476 --> 00:05:40.614
serve with nan.

